<section id="pyramids" class="level1">
<h1>pyramids</h1>
<p>To get a better sense of our population in 2021, we’ll make 3 pyramids for the total by age group, a facet by nationality, and a per capita by nationality graph.</p>
<section id="population-by-age-group" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="population-by-age-group">population by age group</h2>
<p>In the grand scheme of things, men outnumber women in Brunei by around 11.4%. What I find particularly interesting is the odd bulge at around 20-45 for men. At this subset, men outnumbered women by an average of about 21.5%, compared to the overall difference per age group of around 4.6%, which suggests an external mechanism.</p>
